      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<h2>Added</h2>\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Add Osaka Region support for Cloud </p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Bug Fixes</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed backup DR page not showing environment filter</li>\n<li>Fixed enabling sp3 by default on Liferay 7.3</li>\n<li>Fixed chown error during backup service restart</li>\n<li>Prevent guest &amp; support users from navigating to /view-vpn page</li>\n<li>Fixed VPN configuration values not being vertically aligned with field labels given a long server url</li>\n<li>Fixed vulnerability in Backup service third-party packages by updating libraries and depedencies</li>\n<li>Fixed Redirect restricted user viewing /settings/delete-vpn to /settings/vpn</li>\n<li>Fixed Feature Flag page - Application Error when filtering with dropdown menu</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
